<section class="benefits-section rv">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-[1500px]">
    <h2 class="benefits-heading rv">
      How the Expert Adds Value <span class="benefits-accent">and&nbsp;When Expertise Is Required</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <div class="ben-card rv">
        <h3 class="ben-title">Investment Structuring</h3>
        <p class="ben-text">Designing personal, corporate and contractual structures aligned with the client's strategic objectives, taking into account taxation, currency control and practical compliance requirements.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card rv">
        <h3 class="ben-title">Cross-Border Structures</h3>
        <p class="ben-text">Advising where a project extends beyond a single jurisdiction: building an integrated legal framework across multiple countries while addressing local regulatory considerations.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card rv">
        <h3 class="ben-title">Sanctions &amp;&nbsp;Verification</h3>
        <p class="ben-text">Navigating regulatory bottlenecks&nbsp;—&nbsp;from updating verification documentation to obtaining approvals and licenses in relevant jurisdictions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card rv">
        <h3 class="ben-title">Negotiations &amp; Representation</h3>
        <p class="ben-text">Managing communication with government authorities, financial institutions and counterparties, supporting the process through to a practical outcome.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ben-card ben-card--wide rv">
        <div class="ben-wide-inner">
          <h3 class="ben-title ben-title--wide">Asset Protection &amp;&nbsp;Restoration of Control</h3>
          <p class="ben-text ben-text--wide">Advising in situations where investors have already encountered asset freezes, loss of control over <abbr title="Controlled Foreign Companies">CFCs</abbr>, or refusals from banks or custodians.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .benefits-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .benefits-accent {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ===== Bento Grid: 4 equal + 1 full-width ===== */
  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .ben-card {
    background: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.1);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 2rem 1.6rem;
    transition: all 0.4s var(--easing-smooth);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .ben-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.3);
    background: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.05);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Wide card spans all 4 columns */
  .ben-card--wide {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    background: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.15);
    padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
  }
  .ben-card--wide:hover {
    background: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(43, 76, 126, 0.35);
  }

  .ben-wide-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ben-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .ben-card:hover .ben-title {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .ben-title--wide {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ben-text {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .ben-text abbr {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .ben-text--wide {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  /* ===== Tablet: 2 columns ===== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .ben-card--wide {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }
  }

  /* ===== Mobile: 1 column ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-section {
      padding: 3.5rem 0;
    }
    .benefits-heading {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }
    .ben-card {
      padding: 1.5rem 1.3rem;
    }
    .ben-card--wide {
      padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .ben-wide-inner {
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
